Package: OMOPCostAnalyser
Type: Package
Title: Package for analysing healthcare costs for OMOP CDM from cohorts defined in OHDSI ATLAS
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Beatrice", "Hellrand",
      email = "beatrice.marja.hellrand@ut.ee",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package was developed as part of a Bachelor's thesis. The primary objective of the package is to provide a reproducible and modular framework for calculating and visualising direct healthcare costs in cohort-based studies. The package assumes that cohorts are defined using ATLAS and that the underlying data conforms to the OMOP CDM. It supports both programmatic analysis through R functions and interactive exploration via a Shiny web application.
